-- Compiling the project:

1) Make sure to add QT += opengl to the pro file or `qmake -project "QT += opengl"`
2) Remove the Test*.cpp and Test*.moc lines from the pro file

-- Testing the project:

1) Make sure to add CONFIG += qtestlib to the pro file or `qmake -project "QT += qtestlib"`
2) Make sure to add QT += opengl to the pro file
3) Remove main.cpp from the SOURCES list in the pro file

